text: Pfarr is a surname. Notable people with this surname include: * Bernd Pfarr (de) (1958–2004), German painter and cartoonist, author of Sondermann * Frederick Pfarr Stamp Jr. (born 1934), American judge * Paul Pfarr, character in March Violets * Robert Pfarr (1920–2006), American cyclist ==See also== * Pfarr Log House, Ohio, United States * Farr (surname)
